  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in House",
    "asOf": "2021-12-16",
    "date": "2023-08-04T15:01:56Z",
    "text": "Providing Our Law Enforcement with Adequate Resources for a Response Act or the POLAR Response Act\n\nThis bill includes a polar vortex as a major disaster for which a declaration of a state of emergency can be made and provides a definition for a disaster-related emergency for purposes of the Department of Defense (DOD) excess personal property program (therefore authorizing DOD to transfer certain personal property for a polar vortex emergency)."
  },
